	* 2.1-1:
	
	HPL_pdinfo.c.patch
	Original configuration's file is named HPL.dat and need to be
	locate in same directory as xhpl's binary. To be distro compliant
	configuration's file is now looked first in ~/.hpl.conf then
	/etc/hpl.conf.
	
	Makefile.patch <http://forge.cbp.ens-lyon.fr/redmine/projects/
	hpl4all/repository/changes/Makefile>
	Modified to allow compiling elsewhere of $HOME/hpl
	
	Make.top <http://forge.cbp.ens-lyon.fr/redmine/projects/hpl4all/
	repository/changes/Make.top>
	Modified to allow compiling elsewhere of $HOME/hpl
	
	/usr/share/doc/hpl/QUICKSTART
	Quick guide to start quickly :)
	
